me.taylorkelly.mywarp.warp

Class EventfulWarpManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
      • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.warp.EventfulWarpManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WarpManager

    public class EventfulWarpManager
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
    Fires events for all warps managed by it. Functional calls are all delegated to an underling WarpManager as required by the decorator pattern, events are implemented on top.

    Events are dispatched in the EventBus given when initializing this WarpManager. Individual warps fire WarpEvents and the manager itself fires WarpAdditionEvents and WarpDeletionEvents when Warps are added to or removed from it. Handlers that want to listen to such events need to register themselves on the EventBus.
